  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327830/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765201207\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327830/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765201207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327830/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765201207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>THE CURE - is a hardcore 3D shooter with surviving elements where you must survive in zombie apocalypse. The main aim is surviving and exploring large locations, looking for different items such as keys, patrons, medical kits. There's one key on the maps which you must find and move to the next level. But be careful and cautious: you will meet various zombies that are hungry and waiting for your death. Save your ammos, explore locations, look for keys, kill zombies. The game will allow you to enjoy the zombie apocalypse atmosphere!</strong><br><br><i>KEY Features:</i><br><br><strong>- The simplest gameplay.<br>- Pixel graphics.<br>- Large and various locations.<br>- Incredible atmosphere.<br>- Cool impressions from the game.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>THE CURE - is a hardcore 3D shooter with surviving elements where you must survive in zombie apocalypse. The main aim is surviving and exploring large locations, looking for different items such as keys, patrons, medical kits. There's one key on the maps which you must find and move to the next level. But be careful and cautious: you will meet various zombies that are hungry and waiting for your death. Save your ammos, explore locations, look for keys, kill zombies. The game will allow you to enjoy the zombie apocalypse atmosphere!</strong><br><br><i>KEY Features:</i><br><br><strong>- The simplest gameplay.<br>- Pixel graphics.<br>- Large and various locations.<br>- Incredible atmosphere.<br>- Cool impressions from the game.</strong>",
